description: Redevelopment involving the demolition of 3 light industrial buildings and the erection of 5 storey building, a 7 storey building and a part 4/part 6 storey building surrounding a central court raised over a car park. The development contains 60 residential units, including 21 units as affordable housing, and 9 B1 office units (varying in size between 23m2 and 195m2) with associated landscaping and works.
